    <story>
     <plot>
      It's 2029, and mutants are almost extinct.  Logan is entrusted to take
      a mutant girl (Laura) north, where she will meet up with other mutant
      kids who have escaped from a biotech corporation and cross the border
      into Canada where they will be granted asylum.  But the people that
      created Laura want her back, and will do anything to stop them.
